# Custom gaps

You can use custom gaps just by declaring new types and `IsGap` values for them.

    import Neat exposing (IsGap)

    type ButtonGroup
        = ButtonGroup Never

    buttonGroup : IsGap ButtonGroup
    buttonGroup =
        IsGap
            { horizontal = 0.6
            , vertical = 0.6
            }

